    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a vital upgrade for this chassis. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the communicative steering and balanced damping characteristic of the M-division. A mechanically robust example with a linear power band and a redline of 8,000 RPM, perfect for the purist driver.",
