    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a blend of performance and comfort that is hard to find. The engine pulls strongly and shifts seamlessly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time fluid changes and preventative maintenance. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish, save for a few minor, inevitable blemishes typical of careful road use. Step inside to a cabin that remains a sanctuary; the premium seating is intact and supportive, and every feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment screen to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates exactly as intended. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any hidden surprises.",
      "price": 33800.0,
