    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and it still runs like a dream. It's the perfect fit for anyone looking for a dependable car that's ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
